        "ReleaseDate": "2026-03-02T00:08:46Z",
        "Description": "Raw Level-0 packed telemetry data for the full mission in FITS files, usually each covering one 90-minute orbit. These files contain the energy and time of arrival for every HXR photon detected. The RHESSI software in SSW is required to unpack the telemetry stream and construct spectra, time profiles, and images from these data.\nFiles are named hsi_yyyymmdd_hhmmss_ver.fits, where the date and time are the start time of the file, and ver is a version number.",
